downloadTitle: Customizing structured diagram content in Visio 2010
downloadDescription: Learn how to extend the capabilities of structured diagrams in Visio 2010 through custom shapes and solutions.

downloadFile.name: Customizing Structured Diagram Content in Visio 2010.docx

detailsSection: Learn how to extend the capabilities of Microsoft Visio structured diagrams. Virtually any two-dimensional shape can be used as a container, list, or callout in Visio 2010. This white paper explains how you can create, automate, and persist your own custom structured diagram shapes and relationships to help manage increasing diagram complexity.
